  "description": "Captions: English\n\nKṛṣṇa is living, growing, developing, dynamic. Nitya-nava-navāyamāna. Nava-yauvana. Nava-yauvanaṁ ca [Bs: 5.33] Always newer, always fresher. Sometimes Guru Mahārāj would say, “Śyāmasundar means ‘eternally green; evergreen’.”\n\n“Beauty Over Power” is a TheoPhilosophical talk show featuring Bhakti Sudhir Goswami. 21st Century Theism. www.youtube.com/BeautyOverPower\nwww.soundcloud.com/BeautyOverPower\nwww.instagram.com/BeautyOverPower\nwww.vk.com/bsgoswami\n\nTo view full video please go to GoswamiTV channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC7jBk_OZq5C0BqJ80v1ZYCA",
